NAME

    Date::Extract::DE - extract dates from german texts

VERSION

    0.0.1

INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Build.PL
        ./Build
        ./Build test
        ./Build install

SYNOPSIS

    use Date::Extract::DE;
    my $parser = Date::Extract::DE->new( reference_date => $reference_date );
    my $dates = $parser->get_dates($text);

DESCRIPTION

    This is a module to extract dates from german text (similar to Date::Extract).

DEPENDENCIES

    Moose, MooseX::ClassAttribute, Date::Range, Date::Simple, DateTime,
    DateTime::Incomplete

BUGS AND LIMITATIONS

    No bugs have been reported.

    Please report any bugs or feature requests at
    https://github.com/apa-it/date-extract-de/issues.

    Be aware that the API for this module will change with each upcoming

